---
title: Pumpkin, Coconut & Paneer Curry with Basmati Rice
description: Pop your uggies on and grab a bowl of this rich, creamy, comforting curry. With golden cubes of paneer (a fresh cheese popular in India that doesn't melt and has a mild, milky flavour), spinach and pumpkin, this gently spiced dish is a delight from start to finish.
